omponent**: `frontend-0` and `frontend-1`\n   - **Reason**: High `rrt_max` and `rrt` values pointing to performance bottlenecks.\n   - **Evidence**: Median `rrt_max` increased from 22517.0 to 60001257.5; `rrt` traces showed similar spikes.\n\n3. **Product Catalog Service Errors**:\n   - **Component**: `productcatalogservice-0` and `productcatalogservice-1`\n   - **Reason**: Spike in both `client_error_ratio` and `error_ratio`.\n   - **Evidence**: Error ratios moved from negligible values to as high as 100.0.\n\n### Observations\nAlthough pods such as `redis-cart-0` mapped to node `aiops-k8s-08`, no significant node-level anomaly directly correlating with the metrics for `node_cpu_usage_rate`, `node_memory_usage_rate`, or `node_filesystem_usage_rate` was detected in the provided metrics data.\n\n### Output JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increase in error_ratio causing service degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error ratio jumped from 0.0 to 31.12\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High rrt_max and rrt indicating latency issues\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Rrt_max grew from 22517.0 to 60001257.5\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client_error_ratio increase leading to service errors\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Client_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 13.33\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nPlease review the findings to address and mitigate the detected issues and potentially examine the network or other hidden areas not represented directly in this analysis."}
